{"type": "article", "id": 63809, "title": "可口可乐做了复联版易拉罐拉环，奥利奥和故宫联名推出中式糕饼 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-05-16T04:43:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 6474, "name": "联名"}, {"id": 8921, "name": "流量"}, {"id": 58602, "name": "麦昆"}, {"id": 2469, "name": "奥利奥"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 68, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190516123002RmyDOAtNiXEI0kU3.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"k4R6\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4372513859208635?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>易烊千玺成为依云品牌全球代言人，</b></a>昨天依云官方微博发布了一张易烊千玺手写的“你好依云”海报预热。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516123025RI0GCbUZiPagO5L6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.523148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905161230258KjNV6bLsikuGPCm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.411246\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"oLtn\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1842477582/4372302466232343\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>古力娜扎成为 Alexander McQueen 首位大中华区代言人，</b></a>她之前曾是 LVMH 集团旗下 Fendi 中国品牌代言人。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905161231417V4s8XegocBNIuZi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333763\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516123059hUKlNHZTB0VMzI4v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"hN5T\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/2789871777/4372498759714040\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>张艺兴也加入王老吉品牌代言人行列，</b></a>和另一位代言人周冬雨共同出镜夏日主题广告片。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516123202mO8Xd3QL2A6HYfBC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.423611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p line=\"I9Wy\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/3283000062/4372302466729545\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>奥利奥和故宫食品合作推出“朕的心意”饼干礼盒，</b></a>包含山楂、绿茶糕、荔香玫瑰糕等 6 种中式风味，还搭配奥利奥玉玺、点心碟等周边。此外，“启饼皇上，奥利奥进宫了”的文案朗朗上口。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516123221ulVEbA9SJKniwZmL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516123222Rg40k2o1adw3OMxt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516123222B5XMywq6YNunoOlt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516123222cR4pz1JImwHBOFVW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905161232220fiVeRjbYs1IKkxZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"z5xv\"><a href=\"https://hypebae.com/2019/5/starbucks-rainbow-tumbler-cup-pride-month-love\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>星巴克为庆祝骄傲月 50 周年推出一款彩虹冷杯。</b></a>美国和加拿大的消费者本月可以 16.95 美元购买到，外观设计成了彩虹色，还配上 “Love” 字样。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516123256xSEpYn7DNj04WK3C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"2vdJ\"><a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av52519015/?redirectFrom=h5 \" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>网易电音品牌放刺出品了支电子音乐纪录片《放了我》。</b></a>片子以家有工厂的音乐人Yaakov（雅各）和林语所处的环境，展示其作品诞生的过程，借此能一窥国内电子音乐圈的状态。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=o0871dordz2\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"gFGk\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/0SMX5W7SPA0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>SodaStream 再次和《权力的游戏》剧组合作发布第 9 支视频<em> Say Goodbye。</em></b></a>演员们日常都在使用一次性塑料瓶，然后意识到该使用更环保的 SodaStream，依然是强调全球塑料污染的危害。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=w08710zznvp\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"PXqh\"><a href=\"https://adage.com/creativity/work/coca-cola-avengers-pin-tabs/2171851\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>可口可乐/巴西在易拉罐拉环设计上做文章。</b></a>拉环设计成了黑寡妇、绿巨人、雷神等 12 个复仇者英雄的头像。拉环还可以重复使用，当做胸针或者是配饰。创意代理商是 WMcCann。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516123623V5tUQnkTZ6i7IKwM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.491667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905161234523KkylEfs78vQ5Dpw.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p line=\"QGWO\"><a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/agencies/disney-prepares-to-review-1-billion-plus-global-media-business/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>迪士尼将于今年秋季启动价值 10 亿美元的全球比稿。</b></a>参与比稿的 5 家代理商分别是点通安吉斯、阳狮、OMD、传立媒体和 Horizo​​n。业务将涉及迪士尼整个投资组合，其中包括 20 世纪福克斯之前所有的资产。</p><p line=\"nOLG\"><a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/agencies/deutsch-lays-off-at-least-5-of-l-a-staff-as-volkswagen-contract-ends/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>IPG 旗下 Deutsch 在洛杉矶办事处裁员 5% 左右。</b></a>这主要是由于去年大众汽车美国区业务比稿失败，负责了 9 年的客户转到了 WPP 手中。目前洛杉矶总雇员在 100 至 150 人之间，裁员总数为双位数，在过去几个月里一直有平缓少量的员工离职。</p><p line=\"lhBG\">题图来自：<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/qs5e05fV1j0?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pablo Merchán Montes</a> on <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/search/photos/oreo?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unsplash</a></p>"}